{
  "texts": [
    "Furthermore, developing specialized training datasets focused on factual accuracy has been instrumental in training models to prioritize verifiable information [43,27,44].",
    "Integrating External APIs for Enhanced Model PerformanceThe integration of external APIs with language models has opened new avenues for enhancing their capabilities, allowing real-time access to updated information and thus significantly improving the relevance and accuracy of generated content [45,46,47,48].",
    "Such integrations also enable models to perform more complex tasks, such as real-time translations, fact-checking, and information retrieval, directly within the generation process [49,50].",
    "The use of APIs for dynamic data sourcing helps models stay current with the latest events and information, addressing one of the major challenges in maintaining the utility of LLMs [8,4,51].",
    "Leveraging APIs for specialized tasks, such as sentiment analysis or entity recognition, has been shown to enhance the models' analytical capabilities [8,52]."
  ]
}